ZH: 子子孙孙，永不停息。
EN: Descendants will continue forever.

ZH: 子子孙孙，后代不可违背。
EN: Descendants should not disobey the ancestors.

ZH: 子子孙孙，代代传承文化。
EN: Descendants should pass down the culture through generations.

ZH: 子子孙孙，共同维护家族荣誉。
EN: Descendants should uphold the family's honor together.

ZH: 子子孙孙，要懂得感恩。
EN: Descendants should know how to be grateful.

ZH: 子子孙孙，皆为家之栋梁。
EN: Descendants are all pillars of the family.

ZH: 子子孙孙，承载着家族的希望。
EN: Descendants carry the hope of the family.

ZH: 子子孙孙，应该珍惜家族的传统。
EN: Descendants should cherish the traditions of the family.

ZH: 子子孙孙，要互相扶持。
EN: Descendants should support each other.

ZH: 子子孙孙，共同守护家园。
EN: Descendants should protect the home together.

ZH: 子子孙孙，代代相传爱与和平。
EN: Descendants pass down love and peace from generation to generation.

ZH: 子子孙孙，共同奋斗，共同成功。
EN: Descendants should work together and succeed together.

ZH: 子子孙孙，要相亲相爱。
EN: Descendants should love and care for each other.

ZH: 子子孙孙，承受着家族的责任。
EN: Descendants bear the responsibility of the family.

ZH: 子子孙孙，传承先辈的智慧。
EN: Descendants inherit the wisdom of their ancestors.

ZH: 子子孙孙，是家族的未来。
EN: Descendants are the future of the family.

ZH: 子子孙孙，应该维护家族的尊严。
EN: Descendants should uphold the dignity of the family.

ZH: 子子孙孙，要继承家族精神。
EN: Descendants should carry on the family spirit.

ZH: 子子孙孙，是家族的延续。
EN: Descendants are the continuation of the family.

ZH: 子子孙孙，永远铭记祖辈的教诲。
EN: Descendants should always remember the teachings of their ancestors.
